ino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-297x236.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-800x636.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-120x95.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-768x611.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-696x553.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/12133808/2021-Battaglin-Portofino-Edizione-Anniversario-road-bike_handmade-Italian-modern-lugged-steel-road-bike-with-full-internal-routing_front-angled-528x420.jpg 528w\"></a></p><p>Can you really put a price on unparalleled Italian road bike craftsmanship like this? Yes, yes you can. And it’s 5000€, for the custom-sized, custom-painted frameset. But that’s really just the beginning. Battaglin will work with you to paint-to-match your seatpost, stem &amp; bar if you want, and they’ll be happy to organize a complete build kit too – whether you want an all-Italian build with Campagnolo or any other suitably premium finishing kit. Get in touch with Officina Battaglin to claim your bike in the limited run.</p><p><a href=\"https://officinabattaglin.com/products/custom-steel-bikes/portofino/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OfficinaBattaglin.com</a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"12dce54baaefcb8d3b8cb2f13601841a3edde159fa1fbfe5ad5b0d67e00bed24","category":"Cycling"}